  "local_port": 50460,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How can I link Instagram to some group in my Facebook?",
  "response": "Linking your Instagram account to a Facebook group allows you to share Instagram posts directly to the group, making it easier to manage and share content across platforms. Here's how you can do it:\n\n---\n\n### **Steps to Link Instagram to a Facebook Group:**\n\n1. **Ensure You're an Admin of the Facebook Group:**\n   - Only admins of a Facebook group can link an Instagram account to it. If you\u2019re not an admin, ask the group admin to grant you admin access.\n\n2. **Link Instagram to Your Facebook Profile:**\n   - Open the **Instagram app** and go to your profile.\n   - Tap the **menu icon (three horizontal lines)** in the top-right corner.\n   - Select **Settings**.\n   - Tap **Accounts Center**.\n   - Under **Accounts and profiles**, tap on your Facebook account (or add it if not already linked).\n   - Follow the prompts to link your Instagram account to your Facebook profile.\n\n3. **Connect Instagram to the Facebook Group:**\n   - Open the **Facebook app** or go to **Facebook.com**.\n   - Navigate to the **group** where you want to link your Instagram account.\n   - Under the group\u2019s settings, look for an option like **Linked Accounts** or **Instagram Sharing**.\n   - Follow the prompts to connect your Instagram account to the group.\n\n4. **Enable Sharing from Instagram to Facebook Group:**\n   - Once linked, you can now share Instagram posts directly to the Facebook group.\n   - When creating a post on Instagram, tap **Audience** or **Tag People**, then select the option to share to your Facebook group.\n\n---\n\n### **Additional Tips:**\n- Ensure your Instagram account is set to **Public** if you want the posts to be visible to everyone in the group.\n- If you don\u2019t see the option to link Instagram to the group, Facebook may have restricted this feature in your region or for your group type.\n\n---\n\nBy following these steps, you can seamlessly share Instagram content to your Facebook group!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
